{"parse":{"title":"Select committee","pageid":533963,"revid":821142628,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>select committee</b> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Committee\" title=\"Committee\">committee</a> made up of a small number of <a href=\"/wiki/Member_of_parliament\" title=\"Member of parliament\">parliamentary members</a> appointed to deal with particular areas or issues originating in the <a href=\"/wiki/Westminster_system\" title=\"Westminster system\">Westminster system</a> of <a href=\"/wiki/Parliamentary_democracy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Parliamentary democracy\">parliamentary democracy</a>. Select committees exist in the <a href=\"/wiki/Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom\" title=\"Parliament of the United Kingdom\">British Parliament</a>, as well as in other parliaments based on the Westminster model, such as those in <a href=\"/wiki/Australia\" title=\"Australia\">Australia</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Canada\" title=\"Canada\">Canada</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Hong_Kong\" title=\"Hong Kong\">Hong Kong</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/India\" title=\"India\">India</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/New_Zealand\" title=\"New Zealand\">New Zealand</a>.\n</p><p>It is a special <a href=\"/wiki/Subcommittee\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Subcommittee\">subcommittee</a> of a legislature or assembly governed under a <a href=\"/wiki/Committee\" title=\"Committee\">committee system</a>, like <i><a href=\"/wiki/Robert%27s_Rules_of_Order\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rules of Order\">Robert's Rules of Order</a></i>. They are often investigative in nature, collecting data or evidence for a law or problem, and will dissolve immediately<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> after they report their findings to their superiors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>These are very common in <a href=\"/wiki/Legislature\" title=\"Legislature\">government legislatures</a>, and are used to solve special problems, hence their name.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Australia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Australia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#India\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">India</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#New_Zealand\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">New Zealand</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#United_Kingdom\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">United Kingdom</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#United_States\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">United States</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Australia\">Australia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Australia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">Main article: <a href=\"/wiki/Australian_Senate_committees#Select_committees\" title=\"Australian Senate committees\">Australian Senate committees \u00a7&#160;Select committees</a></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"India\">India</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: India\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Under Rule 125 of the <a href=\"/wiki/Rajya_Sabha\" title=\"Rajya Sabha\">Rajya Sabha</a> Rules and Procedures, any member may move as an amendment that a bill be referred to a select committee and, if the motion is carried, the bill shall be referred to such a committee. The House decides the members of such committee.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"New_Zealand\">New Zealand</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: New Zealand\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">Main article: <a href=\"/wiki/New_Zealand_House_of_Representatives_committees\" title=\"New Zealand House of Representatives committees\">New Zealand House of Representatives committees</a></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"United_Kingdom\">United Kingdom</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: United Kingdom\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">Main article: <a href=\"/wiki/Select_committee_(United_Kingdom)\" title=\"Select committee (United Kingdom)\">Select committee (United Kingdom)</a></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"United_States\">United States</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: United States\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">Main article: <a href=\"/wiki/Select_or_special_committee\" title=\"Select or special committee\">Select or special committee</a></div>\n<p>In the <a href=\"/wiki/United_States\" title=\"United States\">United States</a>, notable select committees include the <a href=\"/wiki/Select_Committee_on_Presidential_Campaign_Activities\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Select Committee on Presidential Campaign Activities\">Select Committee on Presidential Campaign Activities</a> (for investigating <a href=\"/wiki/Senate_Watergate_Committee\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Senate Watergate Committee\">Nixon's role in Watergate</a>) and the Select Committee on Benghazi.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/United_States_congressional_committee\" title=\"United States congressional committee\">United States congressional committee</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Special_prosecutor\" title=\"Special prosecutor\">Special prosecutor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Standing_committee\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Standing committee\">Standing committee</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Select_committee&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div c